beer.beer_name: Nut It Out - Walnut, Coffee & Ginseng Pastry Stout - Special Release in collaboration with Quiz Meisters
beer.beer_description:
Special Release Beer Style: Walnut, Coffee & Ginseng Pastry Stout
In collaboration with Quiz Meisters

This stout has some real ZIP about it thanks to the fresh cold brew coffee and ginseng hit, rounded out by toasted roast walnuts.

It's perfect for the wildcard on your team who's just a little bit nutty but always good for morale and really niche topics!

items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 220 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 45!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 180 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 37!

Porters and Stouts are rich with both history and flavor. Roasty, dark, and delicious, these two styles helped start it all. That’s 20 different beers with the style of Porter or Stout. Try 5 more for Level 5!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 205 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 42.
